"Wolf Camp Puyallup - Intro & Advanced Wilderness Survival",outdoor,8,15,2026-08-03,2026-08-07,1710 12th Ave SW,Puyallup,WA,98371,"Combined intro and advanced wilderness survival day camp running concurrently at Clark's Creek Park South Shelter and Blue Skye Farm. Campers without prerequisites join the intro track while returning campers can take the advanced wilderness survival track. Daily schedule 9:00am to 3:45pm with morning lessons, lunch with games and archery, and afternoon activities. 6:1 student-teacher ratio.","$495 full tuition (sliding scale available)",day,all,open,blueskyefarmschool@gmail.com,(425) 248-0253,https://wolfcamp.org/youth/summer-day-camps-for-kids/puyallup-tacoma/,FALSE,FALSE,camp,,,high
"Wolf Camp Puyallup - Advanced Herbal Medicine, Cooking & Craft",outdoor,8,15,2026-08-17,2026-08-21,1710 12th Ave SW,Puyallup,WA,98371,"Advanced herbal medicine, wild cooking, and traditional craft day camp at Clark's Creek Park South Shelter and Blue Skye Farm in Puyallup. Prerequisite is the Wild Cooking & Herbology week, the family ethnobotany workshop, or two prior day camps or family workshops. Daily schedule 9:00am to 3:45pm. 6:1 student-teacher ratio.","$495 full tuition (sliding scale available)",day,advanced,open,blueskyefarmschool@gmail.com,(425) 248-0253,https://wolfcamp.org/youth/summer-day-camps-for-kids/puyallup-tacoma/,FALSE,FALSE,camp,,,high
